{"tid":1642340,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"維基百科(Wiki)撰寫師訓練班：新手任務區","createTime":"2019-10-09T16:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T02:33:25.000Z","uid":71237,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5f66cac960aad7168b85adfaa848f34f0cb4f19c","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我之前開咗一個post介紹維基百科的基本玩法。<br />\n我希望每位有心想寫維基百科嘅人可以睇咗佢先。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n為咗給新人更多練習機會，我決定提供一些新手任務比大家嘗試去寫。<br />\n我會不定期貼啲容易寫嘅嘢上嚟，大家需要做嘅就係：<br />\n1. 入去維基百科寫幾句<br />\n2. 喺段落後面貼資料來源<br />\n<br />\n如果有人完成咗任務，我就會幫手睇下有冇嘢可以改善。如果隔一段時間都無人接任務，我就會自己寫返。喺以上兩種情況我都會喺連登講返任務狀態，大家睇「引用回覆」就可以知道最新情況。<br />\n<br />\n因為我會不斷update依個post，所以如果你想查看最新任務，可以直接去最後果頁睇。<br />\n同埋你可以喺連登用「追故模式」，咁就淨係睇到我的留言。<br />\n<br />\n建議大家寫之前喺維基百科開個新account先，否則會比人知道你的IP address。你唔開account我亦都唔可以喺維基留言比你。<br />\n記得account名唔好一眼比人睇得出你的立場，例如唔好叫「林鄭下台」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n引用資料的教學：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b6L0d93.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb6L0d93.gif&h=ba9c7b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGkGH5P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGkGH5P.gif&h=23d6ce9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4d24e4e35d7c1a21e1fec43b8e60d80b919a928","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"任務：2019年10月3日發生的事件<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpEaTtO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpEaTtO.png&h=48c1e1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似圖中所見，目前10月3日的事件全部淨係得1句，而且全部都無資料來源。<br />\n<br />\n你需要進入以下鏈結進行新手任務：<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動過程_(2019年10月)#10月3日\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B_%282019%E5%B9%B410%E6%9C%88%29%2310%E6%9C%883%E6%97%A5&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5zH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=dc235629\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動過程_(2019年10月)#10月3日</a><br />\n<br />\n新手任務（做到幾多得幾多，就算你淨係寫一句已經幫到手）：<br />\n1. 幫手擴充內容。<br />\n- 有邊位民主派人士接邵家臻及黃浩銘出獄？佢地唱咗邊首反修例歌曲？<br />\n- 香港旅遊發展局以甚麼理由取消美酒巡禮及單車節？<br />\n- 警察到底修改咗咩指引？修改內容係咩？<br />\n- 邊間傳媒、邊個人透露政府計劃訂立反蒙面法？<br />\n<br />\n2. 加內部連結<br />\n而家「美酒巡禮」及「單車節」都欠缺「內部連結」，請你幫手加返。<br />\n我要click入去就link去到「香港美酒佳餚巡禮」及「香港單車節」。<br />\n<br />\n3. 補充資料來源<br />\n圖中每一句後面都需要加資料來源。<br />\n請你去各大報章（例如明報、香港經濟日報、蘋果日報、香港01）搵一兩條關於依件事嘅link，然後按照#1引用資料的教學貼返條link。"},{"pid":"b3766549e4238314390b6f346479b31798c30a5e","tid":1642340,"uid":299376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:29:05.000Z","msg":"721 831 <br />\n推一下"},{"pid":"a2abb2fd2b1830b624cc11bca988b8390ddd2b3a","tid":1642340,"uid":209703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:54:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffa2b9c938259a201ccc8a8ec449faf72fbaa93","tid":1642340,"uid":51411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:04:30.000Z","msg":"Twitter同呢到兩邊都要出力"},{"pid":"89968170d645b91e62a5e6319ddc4bb8aaf92601","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cb84546228eaf6afb25b5f54d2c6ce698260ad8","tid":1642340,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"今晚會試下！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f168ebb224ec76116e94c0847c789e3ec88873","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"任務：守護孩子行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/守護孩子行動\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5zH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=71b304ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/守護孩子行動</a><br />\n而家「守護孩子行動」條目的內容唔多，有待大家幫手擴充。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WPvxq9T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWPvxq9T.png&h=a68c185b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任務內容：<br />\n- 「守護孩子行動」係幾時成立？（6月？7月？有冇確實日期？）<br />\n- Yellow object事件到底係邊一日發生？<br />\n- 有冇成員曾經被捕？幾時、以甚麼罪名被拘捕？<br />\n- 可唔可以幫上圖最後一句「輿論均擔心古稀之年的陳伯會嚴重受傷」加返參考來源？邊個人曾經表示過擔心陳伯？<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/守護孩子行動\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5zH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=71b304ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/守護孩子行動</a>"},{"pid":"5efdcba67dc80c928250a7c5c76b3e5ad70a5055","tid":1642340,"uid":5791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:45:37.000Z","msg":"呢個要推"},{"pid":"b4cc79ed9e888221ac11e11aa17099ea7f544208","tid":1642340,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:49:10.000Z","msg":"用Github啦，唔好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e286e84f876ec36651c8d31360c5ed2e4038f16","tid":1642340,"uid":62402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:53:24.000Z","msg":"呢個要推wor!! 和理非要做！！"},{"pid":"d4c5abe54ab01bd7f16e6c8a563466b7a899dbfa","tid":1642340,"uid":275435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:53:55.000Z","msg":"【突發】繼連儂人後又一力作：連儂布鞋！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1642309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1642309</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a738a3252b45504ddb47509e177d56f1d43fcc7d","tid":1642340,"uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:45:27.000Z","msg":"撰寫師全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bda63db5160200e3c7c8f80a1f3604a8ddd1c8","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:15:00.000Z","msg":"新手任務：歐陽伯權<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/歐陽伯權#出任嶺大校董會高層\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%AD%90%E9%99%BD%E4%BC%AF%E6%AC%8A%23%E5%87%BA%E4%BB%BB%E5%B6%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E8%91%A3%E6%9C%83%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5zH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=ea1140a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/歐陽伯權#出任嶺大校董會高層</a><br />\n歐陽伯權提早離任嶺南大學校董會主席依件事仲未update。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bgScskz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbgScskz.png&h=4a1bff3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任務內容：<br />\n- 清楚交代佢離任的日期<br />\n- 邊個機構曾經提及佢離任原因？佢聲稱的離任原因係咩？<br />\n- 其他人對佢離任有咩反應？<br />\n- 新聞提到佢係提早離任，咁佢本身應該幾時離任？<br />\n（唔一定全部寫哂，就算你寫一句已經有貢獻）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/歐陽伯權#出任嶺大校董會高層\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%AD%90%E9%99%BD%E4%BC%AF%E6%AC%8A%23%E5%87%BA%E4%BB%BB%E5%B6%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E8%91%A3%E6%9C%83%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5zH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=ea1140a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/歐陽伯權#出任嶺大校董會高層</a>"},{"pid":"66bd885fbf2a4a9ffcecf6bf1af6bc20820e2be0","tid":1642340,"uid":56541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:19:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"508c4062d669fabbf01f618d5a54da763a22f980","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4d24e4e35d7c1a21e1fec43b8e60d80b919a928","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"任務：2019年10月3日發生的事件<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpEaTtO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpEaTtO.png&h=48c1e1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似圖中所見，目前10月3日的事件全部淨係得1句，而且全部都無資料來源。<br />\n<br />\n你需要進入以下鏈結進行新手任務：<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動過程_(2019年10月)#10月3日\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B_%282019%E5%B9%B410%E6%9C%88%29%2310%E6%9C%883%E6%97%A5&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5zH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=dc235629\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動過程_(2019年10月)#10月3日</a><br />\n<br />\n新手任務（做到幾多得幾多，就算你淨係寫一句已經幫到手）：<br />\n1. 幫手擴充內容。<br />\n- 有邊位民主派人士接邵家臻及黃浩銘出獄？佢地唱咗邊首反修例歌曲？<br />\n- 香港旅遊發展局以甚麼理由取消美酒巡禮及單車節？<br />\n- 警察到底修改咗咩指引？修改內容係咩？<br />\n- 邊間傳媒、邊個人透露政府計劃訂立反蒙面法？<br />\n<br />\n2. 加內部連結<br />\n而家「美酒巡禮」及「單車節」都欠缺「內部連結」，請你幫手加返。<br />\n我要click入去就link去到「香港美酒佳餚巡禮」及「香港單車節」。<br />\n<br />\n3. 補充資料來源<br />\n圖中每一句後面都需要加資料來源。<br />\n請你去各大報章（例如明報、香港經濟日報、蘋果日報、香港01）搵一兩條關於依件事嘅link，然後按照#1引用資料的教學貼返條link。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"我見到依一項任務已經完成咗啦。<br />\n雖然我無法判斷寫嘅人到底有冇睇過依個post，同埋都唔一定係新手寫。不過我都姑且評論下啦。<br />\n<br />\n「中大罷課遊行」一段有啲句子係直接copy立場新聞，我幫手做咗啲改動。<br />\n大家可以見到短短一日之內條目的質素已經提升咗好多，比我預期中好好多。感謝大家的貢獻！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/252724G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F252724G.png&h=bd0d9cc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d31c45f9a7cd19fd355780d5abd2e19ebf89528","tid":1642340,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:28:29.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cd8711546634ffbf0ff20b44f669fc9043862c","tid":1642340,"uid":14296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:32:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ea479756a8d0ffccb6b554afef84c812a5ce745","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:21:13.000Z","msg":"招募資料搜集師！！<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔想做撰寫師，但係又想出一分力，你可以幫手做資料搜集師。<br />\n有人喺維基百科開咗一頁專門收集新聞。<br />\n<br />\n如果你發現有嘢值得寫落維基百基<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而仲未有人寫</span></strong>，你可以將相關的新聞連結放喺依一頁。咁做可以節省其他撰寫師搜集資料的時間。<br />\n<a href=\"https://w.wiki/9tA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fw.wiki%2F9tA&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5zH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=9b1d3fe1\" target=\"_blank\">https://w.wiki/9tA</a>"},{"pid":"623d6323268b30718ff611f40dcecd23e1cda46f","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ea479756a8d0ffccb6b554afef84c812a5ce745","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:21:13.000Z","msg":"招募資料搜集師！！<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔想做撰寫師，但係又想出一分力，你可以幫手做資料搜集師。<br />\n有人喺維基百科開咗一頁專門收集新聞。<br />\n<br />\n如果你發現有嘢值得寫落維基百基<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而仲未有人寫</span></strong>，你可以將相關的新聞連結放喺依一頁。咁做可以節省其他撰寫師搜集資料的時間。<br />\n<a href=\"https://w.wiki/9tA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fw.wiki%2F9tA&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5zH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=9b1d3fe1\" target=\"_blank\">https://w.wiki/9tA</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:34:53.000Z","msg":"如果你係撰寫師，想其他人幫手搜集資料，可以喺入面講聲。<br />\n等資料搜集員幫手搵資料來源。"},{"pid":"72cd1acd58d9514be65f1f11539214685f7a783e","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T13:41:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0e5824e669b2ef6f0e96cb215a5a03dd134deb1","tid":1642340,"uid":74783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:18:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b036decd9107f07238f3cbda9eba3fc964516f72","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3f168ebb224ec76116e94c0847c789e3ec88873","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"任務：守護孩子行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/守護孩子行動\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5zH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=71b304ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/守護孩子行動</a><br />\n而家「守護孩子行動」條目的內容唔多，有待大家幫手擴充。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WPvxq9T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWPvxq9T.png&h=a68c185b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任務內容：<br />\n- 「守護孩子行動」係幾時成立？（6月？7月？有冇確實日期？）<br />\n- Yellow object事件到底係邊一日發生？<br />\n- 有冇成員曾經被捕？幾時、以甚麼罪名被拘捕？<br />\n- 可唔可以幫上圖最後一句「輿論均擔心古稀之年的陳伯會嚴重受傷」加返參考來源？邊個人曾經表示過擔心陳伯？<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/守護孩子行動\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5zH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=71b304ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/守護孩子行動</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:34:36.000Z","msg":"守護孩子行動的條目已經大幅改善，清楚記錄返組成的理念、過程。<br />\n感謝各位的貢獻！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U9Yjvsj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU9Yjvsj.png&h=6b9ce66c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9a5d48c9630c3664ece65247f83356981204d29","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50bda63db5160200e3c7c8f80a1f3604a8ddd1c8","tid":1642340,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:15:00.000Z","msg":"新手任務：歐陽伯權<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/歐陽伯權#出任嶺大校董會高層\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%AD%90%E9%99%BD%E4%BC%AF%E6%AC%8A%23%E5%87%BA%E4%BB%BB%E5%B6%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E8%91%A3%E6%9C%83%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5zH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=ea1140a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/歐陽伯權#出任嶺大校董會高層</a><br />\n歐陽伯權提早離任嶺南大學校董會主席依件事仲未update。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bgScskz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbgScskz.png&h=4a1bff3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任務內容：<br />\n- 清楚交代佢離任的日期<br />\n- 邊個機構曾經提及佢離任原因？佢聲稱的離任原因係咩？<br />\n- 其他人對佢離任有咩反應？<br />\n- 新聞提到佢係提早離任，咁佢本身應該幾時離任？<br />\n（唔一定全部寫哂，就算你寫一句已經有貢獻）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/歐陽伯權#出任嶺大校董會高層\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%AD%90%E9%99%BD%E4%BC%AF%E6%AC%8A%23%E5%87%BA%E4%BB%BB%E5%B6%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E8%91%A3%E6%9C%83%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5zH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=ea1140a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/歐陽伯權#出任嶺大校董會高層</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"依一個任務都順利完成咗！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oije3Oj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foije3Oj.png&h=5b2ea022&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88b74b0fb68298e0ebae3c7c679971f10006e6a6","tid":1642340,"uid":204205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:37:20.000Z","msg":"推"}]}